      "platform": "x",
      "text": "Hahahahaha\n\n\nOSZ (@OpenSourceZone)\n\nAmong Republicans do you agree with Trump or Carlson and Kelly on foreign policy views\n\n\ud83d\udd34 Trump: 84%\n\ud83d\udfe1 Carlson/Kelly: 6%\n\nJ.L. Partners poll | 3/17-18 | 1,018 LV\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\u2014 https://nitter.net/OpenSourceZone/status/2034621722754990093#m",
      "sourceUrl": "https://x.com/MeghanMcCain/status/2034650311831232704",
      "timestamp": "2026-03-19T15:16:50+00:00",
      "type": "tweet"
    },
    {
      "voiceId": "meghan-mccain",
      "voiceName": "Meghan McCain",
      "platform": "x",
      "text": "I was a cohost on the view for 4 years and this is the most unhinged, insane segment of political media I have ever seen in my entire life. \n\nOur friend @benfergusonshow is too good for this batshit insanity.\n\n\nEyal Yakoby (@EYakoby)\n\nBREAKING: Cenk Uygur has an insane meltdown on Piers Morgan and begins screaming and cursing while veins pop out of his forehead.\n\nCompletely unhinged.\n\nVideo\n  \n\n\n\n\n\n\u2014 https://nitter.net/EYakoby/status/2034424475886748064#m",
      "sourceUrl": "https://x.com/MeghanMcCain/status/2034457010004017542",
      "timestamp": "2026-03-19T02:28:44+00:00",
      "type": "tweet"
    },
    {
      "voiceId": "meghan-mccain",
      "voiceName": "Meghan McCain",
      "platform": "x",
      "text": "HAHAHAHA morning tv is so asinine!!!! Also props to this actress for her answer.\n\n\nVaughn Sterling (@vplus)\n\nI will never cut the cord. Television forever.\n\nVideo\n  \n\n\n\n\n\n\u2014 https://nitter.net/vplus/status/2034251960858050963#m",
      "sourceUrl": "https://x.com/MeghanMcCain/status/2034335684916297959",
      "timestamp": "2026-03-18T18:26:38+00:00",
      "type": "tweet"
    },
    {
      "voiceId": "meghan-mccain",
      "voiceName": "Meghan McCain",
      "platform": "x",
      "text": "There is hands down no one else I trust more to keep our homeland safe and to be in charge of our national security than \u2066@TulsiGabbard\u2069.\n\n\ud83c\uddfa\ud83c\uddf8\ud83c\uddfa\ud83c\uddf8\ud83c\uddfa\ud83c\uddf8",
      "sourceUrl": "https://x.com/MeghanMcCain/status/2034289432711307429",
      "timestamp": "2026-03-18T15:22:50+00:00",
      "type": "tweet"
    },
    {
      "voiceId": "meghan-mccain",
      "voiceName": "Meghan McCain",
      "platform": "x",
      "text": "HELL YEAH!!!!!\n\n\nInsider Wire (@InsiderWire)\n\n#BREAKING: \ud835\udd4f will soon let users restrict both posts and replies by region or country.\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\u2014 https://nitter.net/InsiderWire/status/2034075067731366137#m",
      "sourceUrl": "https://x.com/MeghanMcCain/status/2034094041034272822",
      "timestamp": "2026-03-18T02:26:25+00:00",
      "type": "tweet"
    },
    {
      "voiceId": "meghan-mccain",
      "voiceName": "Meghan McCain",
      "platform": "x",
      "text": "For whatever it is worth Jerry, we have known each other socially for a long time - you have always been so kind and respectful (as has your wife). You aren't one of those people who treat republicans like they are going to infect you with a conservative disease. \n\nThese are very tough times, give yourself grace. Talking publicly about politics aint for the weak of heart and it's taken me 20 years to be immune to all the punches. The one and only time I went on Bill Mahers show when I was 24 I c",
      "sourceUrl": "https://x.com/MeghanMcCain/status/2034066480044904739",
      "timestamp": "2026-03-18T00:36:54+00:00",
      "type": "tweet"
    },
    {
      "voiceId": "meghan-mccain",
      "voiceName": "Meghan McCain",
      "platform": "x",
      "text": "Being hated by idiots is the price you pay for not being one of them.",
      "sourceUrl": "https://x.com/MeghanMcCain/status/2033998333941789141",
      "timestamp": "2026-03-17T20:06:07+00:00",
      "type": "tweet"
