      "voiceName": "Meghan McCain",
      "platform": "x",
      "text": "WOW!!\n\n\nYashar Ali \ud83d\udc18 (@yashar)\n\nBREAKING \n\nIsrael says it has killed Ali Larijani, the de facto leader of the Islamic Republic of Iran and Gholamreza Soleimani, the head of the Basij, the infamous paramilitary force that the regime uses to suppress protests and control civilians.\n\nIn January, Larijani was said to have overseen the crackdown on protesters that resulted in many thousands of Iranians being killed in the streets by the regime and many more being imprisoned.\n\nFull Story: bit.ly/4rzuE",
